data.description: Back on market due to buyer financing.  Welcome to this beautifully maintained 2016 single-story residence, boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and modern amenities tailored for the contemporary homeowner. As you step inside, you're greeted by an open-concept living area that seamlessly blends style and functionality, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. Retreat to the expansive master suite with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom featuring dual vanities and a luxurious soaking tub. Enjoy the Texas sun in the landscaped backyard—perfect for barbecues and family gatherings.
